    <body>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <p xml:id="NA378-kiḷavi">1. itu tōḻi ciṟaippuṟamākac colliyatu. 2. talaimaka ṉoruvaḻit taṇantapiṉṉai vaṉpoṟai yetirmoḻintatūumām.</p>
        <p xml:lang="en">1. This is what the confidante said when [HE] was behind the fence. 2. It is also how [SHE] was desolate in the face of consolation after HE had departed on a temporary absence.</p>
        </div>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <lg xml:id="NA378">
<l>yāmamu neṭiya kaḻiyuṅ kāmamuṅ</l>
<l>kaṇpaṭa līyātu perukun teṇkaṭaṉ</l>
<l>muḻaṅkutirai muḻaviṉ pāṇiyiṟ paipayap</l>
<l>paḻampuṇ ṇuṟunariṟ paravaiyi ṉālu</l>
<l>māṅkavai naliyavu nīṅki yāṅku</l>
<l>miraviṟan tellai tōṉṟala talarvā</l>
<l>yayaliṟ peṇṭir pacalai pāṭa</l>
<l>vīṅkā kiṉṟāṟ ṟōḻi yōṅkumaṇal</l>
<l>variyār ciṟumaṉai citaii vantu</l>
<l>parivutarat toṭṭa paṇimoḻi nampip</l>
<l>pāṭimiḻ paṉinīrc cērppaṉoṭu</l>
<l>nāṭā tiyainta naṇpiṉa taḷavē.</l>
            </lg>
        <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>          Midnight is passing by for a long time and desire is</l>
<l rend="indent">          increasing without granting the eyes to close.</l>
<l rend="indent4">          The thundering waves<note place="foot">Actually we would expect another coordination here. But perhaps another -<term xml:lang="ta">um</term> was not possible for metrical reasons. In any case, it also seems possible to read three dependant temporal <term xml:lang="ta">peyareccam</term> clauses.</note></l>
<l>        of the clear sea are playing in the expanse, gently,</l>
<l rend="indent">          as the beat of a drum, as those having an old wound –</l>
<l rend="indent">          even while those are thus afflicting [me], as though it had left,</l>
<l>        having crossed the night, the daylight won’t appear.</l>
<l rend="indent4">          While gossip-mouthed</l>
<l>        women from the neighbourhood sing [my] pallor,</l>
<l>        it has indeed become thus, friend:</l>
<l>        the limit of the friendship enjoyed without examination</l>
<l rend="indent2">          with the man from the coast of chilly waters buzzing with singing,</l>
<l rend="indent">          trusting [his] humble words that touched [me] movingly(?),</l>
<l rend="indent2">          coming [and] spoiling the small houses full of lines in the high sand.</l>
        </lg>
      </div>
    </body>
